{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://Vinnl.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"Grand Opera House (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that a brewery was responsible for commissioning Philadelphia's <b><a href=\"/wiki/Grand_Opera_House_(Philadelphia)\" title=\"Grand Opera House (Philadelphia)\">Grand Opera House</a></b> <i>(pictured)</i><span style=\"padding-left:0.15em;\">?</span>","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grand_Opera_House_(Philadelphia)","retrieved":1777621289430},{"title":"Seraphina Beh (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Seraphina_Beh\" title=\"Seraphina Beh\">Seraphina Beh</a></b> landed a role on <i><a href=\"/wiki/EastEnders\" title=\"EastEnders\">EastEnders</a></i> after a producer saw her perform in <i><a href=\"/wiki/Pigeon_English\" title=\"Pigeon English\">Pigeon English</a></i><span style=\"padding-left:0.15em;\">?</span>","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seraphina_Beh","retrieved":1777621289431},{"title":"a 1920s Muslim women's magazine (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Isteri_Soesila%E2%80%93Taman_Moeslimah\" title=\"Isteri Soesila–Taman Moeslimah\">a 1920s Muslim women's magazine</a></b> highlighted women in the Philippines as examples of modern womanhood?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isteri_Soesila%E2%80%93Taman_Moeslimah","retrieved":1777621289432},{"title":"Russia 200 (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that photographs of Russian soldiers killed in Ukraine were arranged to form a mosaic image of <a href=\"/wiki/Vasily_Vereshchagin\" title=\"Vasily Vereshchagin\">Vasily Vereshchagin</a>'s <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Apotheosis_of_War\" title=\"The Apotheosis of War\">The Apotheosis of War</a></i> on <b><a href=\"/wiki/Russia_200\" title=\"Russia 200\">Russia&nbsp;200</a></b><span class=\"nowrap\">'s</span> website?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Russia_200","retrieved":1777621289434},{"title":"Vivinos (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that an anime ending sequence by <b><a href=\"/wiki/Vivinos\" title=\"Vivinos\">Vivinos</a></b>, featuring <b><a href=\"/wiki/Kawaii_Kaiwai\" title=\"Kawaii Kaiwai\">a song</a></b> from <b><a href=\"/wiki/Karen_Matsumoto\" title=\"Karen Matsumoto\">Karen Matsumoto</a></b> and <b><a href=\"/wiki/Haruka_Sakuraba\" title=\"Haruka Sakuraba\">Haruka Sakuraba</a></b><span class=\"nowrap\">'s</span> unit <b><a href=\"/wiki/PiKi\" title=\"PiKi\">PiKi</a></b>, was compared to a \"snowglobe that swirls with pink glitter\"?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vivinos","retrieved":1777621289435},{"title":"killing of Joetha Collier (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that Richard Nixon ordered the FBI to investigate the <b><a href=\"/wiki/Killing_of_Joetha_Collier\" title=\"Killing of Joetha Collier\">killing of Joetha Collier</a></b> after civil rights activist <a href=\"/wiki/Aaron_Henry_(politician)\" title=\"Aaron Henry (politician)\">Aaron Henry</a> telegraphed him about the incident?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Killing_of_Joetha_Collier","retrieved":1777621289437},{"title":"Invisible Woman (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that an advertisement featuring the <b><a href=\"/wiki/Invisible_Woman_(Marvel_Rivals)\" title=\"Invisible Woman (Marvel Rivals)\">Invisible Woman</a></b> from <i>Marvel Rivals</i> was found in breach of advertising ethics by the Ad Standards Community Panel in Australia?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Invisible_Woman_(Marvel_Rivals)","retrieved":1777621289438},{"title":"quotas for transgender people (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that some universities in Brazil have <b><a href=\"/wiki/Transgender_quotas_in_Brazil\" title=\"Transgender quotas in Brazil\">quotas for transgender people</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transgender_quotas_in_Brazil","retrieved":1777621289440},{"title":"Menches (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that archaeologists fou